description: This skill is meant to add computer science-related jokes to Alexa's nerdbank. There are currently 51 possible jokes, with more on the horizon. Jokes++ will also expand out into other nerdy categories, such as movies, television shows, and comic books.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Jokes Plus Plus for a computer science joke.
Alexa, ask Jokes Plus Plus to tell me a joke.
Alexa, tell Jokes Plus Plus to give me a good programming joke.
name: Jokes++: Computer Science Jokes
shortDescription: An expansion of Alexa's cheesy jokes for all you CS majors out there.
